                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am an officer; on the 28th of December last, I and Warren went to Stevens's house, in Lambeth; he is a greengrocer; we searched his apartments, and found this great coat. (Produces it.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18020113-65-person677">
